  Locus:
    Page: 406
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Search/Look Within
---
If we pursue spiritual illumination, it will fade away. If we separate
ourselves from God as the doer, we become the searcher, always haunted and
always trying to find the ultimate Reality. We neither seek it nor look for
it, for all we want is here, now.
